OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1783669804
OL,3,CNew police speed trap devices unveiled
OL,5,FA new PSNI pilot programme will see
OL,6,Fhand-held cameras equipped with laser
OL,7,Fand video capability used to catch
OL,8,Fspeeding motorists in Northern Ireland.
OL,10,FThe new mobile cameras can detect a
OL,11,Fspeeding vehicle from a distance of up
OL,12,Fto one kilometre and can be deployed
OL,13,Fon any road.
OL,15,FThree Trucam II cameras, a hand-held
OL,16,Fequivalent to the safety camera vans,
OL,17,Fwill be deployed over the next three
OL,18,Fmonths as part of the initiative.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/8
