PN,41802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1783669804
OL,3,CNew police speed trap devices unveiled
OL,5,FThe PSNI is running the project with
OL,6,Fthe Northern Ireland Road Safety
OL,7,FPartnership (NIRSP).
OL,9,FThe cameras combine a speed-detecting
OL,10,Flaser with a video recording function,
OL,11,Fand can capture the information needed
OL,12,Fto prosecute drivers speeding without
OL,13,Fthem stopping.
OL,15,FThe cameras can be used on roads where
OL,16,Froad safety vans cannot be deployed.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
