PN,41803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1783669804
OL,3,CNew police speed trap devices unveiled
OL,5,FHead of the PSNI's Road Policing Unit
OL,6,FChief Inspector Celeste Simpson said:
OL,7,F"Working with the Road Safety
OL,8,FPartnership, we are committed to
OL,9,Fchanging driver behaviour, improve
OL,10,Froad safety and deliver Operation
OL,11,FLifesaver to tackle speeding.
OL,13,F"We often hear police aren't doing
OL,14,Fenough to tackle speeding on our
OL,15,Froads, especially on rural roads.
OL,17,F"Having these cameras means we reach
OL,18,Fthose roads where it isn't suitable to
OL,19,Fdeploy NIRSP safety camera vans, where
OL,20,Fthere's a proven history of collisions
OL,21,Fand where there is community concern.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,419,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1783669804
OL,3,CNew police speed trap devices unveiled
OL,5,F"These cameras, for use initially by
OL,6,Four Road Policing Unit officers, can
OL,7,Ftravel anywhere, at any time, on any
OL,8,Froad across Northern Ireland and can
OL,9,Foperate during hours of darkness."
OL,11,FMs Simpson added: "They can record
OL,12,Fmoving footage and provide a high-
OL,13,Fdefinition image which can be
OL,14,Fprocessed without the need to stop the
OL,15,Fvehicles at the scene, streamlining
OL,16,Fthe process of speed enforcement.
OL,18,F"They can detect speeding vehicles
OL,19,Ffrom distances up to one kilometre
OL,20,Fand, for anyone speeding, by the time
OL,21,Fthey've seen it, it will be too late.
OL,26,@mD@AOUqD@bO]sD@SOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
