FL,419,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1783669804
OL,3,CNew police speed trap devices unveiled
OL,5,F"They will have been detected and
OL,6,Freceive a notification in the post,
OL,7,Fthe same as if detected by NIRSP
OL,8,Fsafety camera vans.
OL,10,F"As well as NIRSP safety camera vans
OL,11,Fand average speed cameras, this state-
OL,12,Fof-the-art technology should serve as
OL,13,Fa deterrent to anyone who thinks
OL,14,Fspeeding is acceptable and they can
OL,15,Fget away with it, especially off the
OL,16,Fmain roads.
OL,26,@mD@AOUrD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/8
