PN,41806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1783669804
OL,3,CNew police speed trap devices unveiled
OL,5,F"We work every day to make our roads
OL,6,Fsafer for everyone and the Trucam II
OL,7,Fcameras will enable us to enforce
OL,8,Fspeed limits more effectively, and
OL,9,Frespond to local priorities and
OL,10,Fconcerns."
OL,12,FSo far 36 people have died in road
OL,13,Fcollisions in Northern Ireland in 2026.
OL,15,FThe senior officer said: "These are
OL,16,Fdevastating losses. Lives changed in
OL,17,Fan instant and forever.
OL,26,@mD@AOUrD@JO]wD@ZOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/8
