FL,419,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1783669804
OL,3,CNew police speed trap devices unveiled
OL,5,F"The number of people dying on our
OL,6,Froads is unacceptably high. Reducing
OL,7,Fserious and fatal collisions is a
OL,8,Fpriority for The Police Service.
OL,9,FTackling excessive speed, one of the
OL,10,Ffatal five, is key to this.
OL,12,F"Our message to everyone on our roads
OL,13,Fis remember the 'fatal five' ` slow
OL,14,Fdown; don't be careless; always wear
OL,15,Fyour seat belt; don't drink or take
OL,16,Fdrugs and drive and never use your
OL,17,Fmobile phone while driving.
OL,26,@mD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/8
