CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1783669804
OL,3,CNew police speed trap devices unveiled
OL,5,F"Together, by making safer choices, we
OL,6,Fcan help keep our roads safer for
OL,7,Feveryone and reduce serious and fatal
OL,8,Froad collisions on our roads."
